    "body" : "<p>ok just my two cents, use a is string method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static boolean isString(Object thing) {\n    return thing instanceof String;\n}\n\npublic void someMethod(Object thing){\n    if (!isString(thing)) {\n        return null;\n    }\n    log.debug(\"my thing is valid\");\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
