    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can achieve by doing below way.. just add a condition by adding bracket <code>if(!(condition with instanceOf))</code> with the whole condition by adding <code>!</code> operator at the start just the way mentioned in below code snippets.</p>\n\n<pre><code>if(!(str instanceof String)) { /* do Something */ } // COMPILATION WORK\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>instead of </p>\n\n<pre><code>if(str !instanceof String) { /* do Something */ } // COMPILATION FAIL\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
